data.description: Located in a peaceful neighborhood on just over half acre, this updated immaculate home offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. You'll enjoy the benefits of small-town living while being just minutes away from schools, parks, and shopping. The master suite is on the first floor; with the option of a large 4th bedroom or bonus room on the second floor. The open floor plan connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, making it perfect for entertaining. Outside, you can enjoy a cup of coffee or large gatherings under the covered deck. This home is move-in ready so you can start making memories! Open House, Sat. Dec. 2nd, 2-4pm
